This field act as a Quick class code. The code specified in this attribute will be generated just after the code-behind class definition.

======== WHEN TO USE/SET IT? ====================

When start up section doesn't fulfil the requirement and you wan to write page level custom code.

======== EXAMPLES ===============================

Example 1

public Member Item { {get{Request.Get (); }}

Example 2

protected override void InitializeCulture()

{

//Culture Initialization Code

}

In this field you should write your custom code. Depending the event you have selected for this custom code, the content of the code should be C#, JS, or CSS code.

======== WHEN TO USE/SET IT? ====================

When you want to add a custom code to the module.

======== EXAMPLES ===============================

public int Index { get { return 0; } }

function Funa() {

alert(&#39;Hello!&#39;);

}

